{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mandate all restaurants with soft play to have qualified first aiders",
        "additional_details": "Accidents have taken place at soft play facilities, including broken arms. Children can be helped sooner if first aid is administered on site, reducing the likelihood of long-term effects.",
        "background": "Introduce legislation so that all family restaurants with soft plays, climbing frames and play parks are required to have a first aider on every shift and a fully stocked first aid box. This could be known as Blakes Law.",
